# Shared Packages

## `@venue-pos/shared`
- `ROLES`, `ORDER_STATUSES`, `API_BASE`, `ERROR_CODES`
- No runtime deps; pure JS exports
- Add new error codes here before using in API

## `@venue-pos/i18n`
- `locales/en.json`, `locales/ar.json` — keep keys identical
- `resources`, `getDirection()`, `supportedLocales`
- Apps wire up react-i18next locally; do not add app-specific strings outside locale files

## When to create a new shared package
Only when **2+ apps** need the same code. Otherwise keep logic in the app.

## Do not put in shared
- Prisma client
- React components (until `packages/ui` is intentionally introduced in Phase 5+)
- Electron or Fastify-specific code
